features: Gentle Care for Your Eyes: Our desk lamp features 56 LED beads that provides soft and non flickering light, helping to prevent eye fatigue even after hours of use. Perfect for people who spend long hours reading, writing, or working in front of the computer. Perfect table lamp for office.

Freely Adjustable Angle and Height: With 2 supporting arms and 5 rotating joints, you can freely adjust the height and angle to cast light in any direction you like. The small desk lamp occupies very little space on the desk, but can illuminate a large area. Up to 1000lm, RA color rendering greater than 85. The desk lights are perfect for bedroom, reading room, office, living room, etc.

Touch Control & Memory Function: The led desk light can be adjusted for brightness levels by sliding your finger, with 5 temperature modes(2800K-6500K) and 5 brightness levels to suit different needs. The desk lamps for home office support a power-off memory function, which can remember your previous color modes and brightness after you turn off the light.

Wireless Charger & USB Charging Port: The desk lamp has a 5V/3A USB port and the latest 10W wireless charging function, making it convenient for you to use. Whether the light is on or not, you can easily charge your phone. No more trouble dealing with wire chaos! A good desk lamp with wireless charging! Also Equipped with a 1.5 meter USB charger and adapter.

Auto Timer / Night Light Function: The led desk lamp has a 60 minutes automatic shutdown timer, which can save power. If you have any questions with the table lamp, please let us know as soon as possible. We will provide professional services in 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We've been wanting a creative, desk lamp for years that can be easily turned and light areas when I'm at my desk. This is that lamp. Bright and reliable, dimmable as well as a charge depot for my iPhone and charges quickly, and also has a night light. Perfect for us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So nice, you'll buy twice!
reviews.reviewText: Sorry for the bad title line, but it's true. I liked mine so much for my office that I bought my son one for his room. I needed some to place behind my computer screens so I can go e myself some facial light during my online meetings. The articulation on the arm makes this a perfect tool to do just that. The color selection and dimming are amazing, and I love how this actually charges my phone's without me removing my cases.I absolutely love this lamp. It's build really well, and looks so nice. I really can't find any flaws with it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Does exactly what I want, light over my desk so I don't have to turn on the overhead room light. And it charges my cell phone! Win-win!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It takes a little bit of effort to put it together
reviews.reviewText: … but it is well worth your time. The overhead bright light is bright, but can be moved around, so it is not directly in your line of sight. The charger really charges, I’ve had a couple that did not. It’s not weighted the way I think it should be. But my partner tells me I am too picky. There may be a reason why I am athe vine reviewer in the family. This would make a great office lamp, but also, it would be very good in the den. It would make a good gift. But put it up high enough that small hands can’t knock it over. They really like to play with the touch control.
